(46, 'Instalação', 'doc', 9, 1, 1, 'instalacao', 15, 51, '2020-05-18 23:57:34', '2020-05-20 23:54:36', 'Instalação do Nopadi MF/NP ', '', NULL, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Nopadi MF/NP não suporta PHP em versões anteriores a 7, pois usa funcionalidades que só estão disponíveis na versão 7 ou superior do PHP. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No momento o Nopadi não está disponível para downloads por se tratar de uma versão de testes para um publico especifico. Mas caso tenha interesse em participar dos testes, você poderá entrar em contato com o desenvolvedor por meio do seguinte endereço de e-mail: pauloleonardo.rio@gmail.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instalação&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(96, 125, 139);&quot;&gt;Recomendamos que você utilize o &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wampserver.com/&quot; title=&quot;Site oficial do WampServer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;WampServer&lt;/a&gt; como servidor para testes locais. Certifique que os módulos específicos do PHP como o modulo de PDO e o modulo de reescrita do Apache estão ativos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Após baixar o Nopadi por meio do link oficial (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 152, 0);&quot;&gt;link não disponível no momento&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; Você irá navegar até o diretório escolhido em seu servidor local, no caso do WampServer o diretório é o www.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Lembrando que você pode usar qualquer outro servidor de sua preferência, ou até mesmo, usar o servidor embutido no PHP via CLI. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;No diretório do Nopadi navegue até a pasta de configuração que fica no seguinte caminho: &lt;em&gt;&#039;set/config&lt;/em&gt;&#039;. Dentro desse diretorio você encontrará dois arquivos PHP de configuração do Nopadi. O mais importante no momento é configurar o arquivo &quot;application.php&quot;, pois ele dará o ponta pé inicial para o bom funcionamento do framework. O arquvio &quot;database.php&quot; só deverá ser configurado caso você queira trabalhar com autenticação de usuários usando a tabela de usuários do Nopadi, pois para isso será necessário configurar a conexão com a sua base de dados por meio desse arquivo. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Arquivo para configurar a execução da aplicação:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;set/config/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;application.php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Arquivo para configurar a conexão com o banco de dados:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;set/config/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;application.php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;Atenção: ao configurar os arquivos na pasta config, os arquivos não podem sofrer alterações nas posições das variáveis nas linhas. Somente o conteúdo das variáveis devem ser alterados, jamais a posição delas referente as linhas. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Arquivo &#039;application.php&#039;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;php\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//URL da aplicação/site Nopadi&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_URL&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;http://localhost/nopadi&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Nome da aplicação Nopadi&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_NAME&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Nopadi&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Descrição da aplicação Nopadi&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_DESCRIPTION&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Um micro framework para todos os projetos&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Palavras chaves da aplicação Nopadi&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_KEY_WORKS&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;php,framework,web,api,rest&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Registra os erros no arquivo de log&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_ERROR_LOG&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Off&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Permitir acesso de domínios externos na aplicação&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_ACCESS_CORS&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;On&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Colocar aplicação em modo de manutenção&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_MODE_MAINTENANCE&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Off&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Colocar aplicação em modo de desenvolvimento&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_MODE_DEV&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Off&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Versão da aplicação&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_VERSION&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;06.03.2020&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Zona de data e hora do ambiente da aplicação&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_LOCAL_TIME&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;America/Sao_Paulo&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Idioma oficial da aplicação&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_LANG&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;pt-br&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Conjunto de caracteres utilizados pela aplicação&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_CHAR_SET&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;UTF-8&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Define se a aplicação já está instalada &lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_INSTALL&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;On&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Arquivo &#039;database.php&#039;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;php\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//URL do servidor do banco de dados&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_HOST&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;localhost&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Nome de usuário do banco de dados&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_USER&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;root&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Senha de usuário de banco de dados&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_PASS&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Nome do banco de dados&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_DBSA&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;nano&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Prefixo da tabela do banco de dados&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_FIX&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;np_&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;//Drive do SGBD&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;NP_SGBD&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;mysql&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;As variáveis de com o valor On ou Off só aceitam um desses dois valores. Já no caso da variável NP_LOCAL_TIME voc&lt;/span&gt;ê poderá consultar no site oficial do PHP a &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 150, 243);&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.php.net/manual/pt_BR/timezones.php&quot; title=&quot;Lista de Fusos Horários Suportados&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Lista de Fusos Horários Suportados&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. Por padrão, a zona configurada é a de São Paulo - Brasil. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;É importante que na váriavel&amp;nbsp; NP_URL o valor corrsponda a URL do seu site, para que a aplicação possa utilizar para buscar os seu recursos internamente. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 87, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 1),
(48, 'teste', 'post', 9, 1, 1, 'teste', 0, 0, '2020-05-19 19:48:14', NULL, '', '', NULL, '&lt;p&gt;cccc&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 0),
(49, 'exemplo', 'post', 9, 1, 1, 'exemplo', 0, 0, '2020-05-20 11:15:08', NULL, '', '', NULL, '&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;div id&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;app&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Preços &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; Bitcoin&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;section v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;errored&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Pedimos desculpas&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; não estamos conseguindo recuperar &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; informações no momento&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; Por favor&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; tente novamente mais tarde&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;section&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 1),
(50, 'exemplox', 'post', 9, 1, 1, 'exemplox', 14, 0, '2020-05-20 11:15:53', NULL, '', '', NULL, '&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;div id&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;app&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Preços &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; Bitcoin&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;h1&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;section v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;errored&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Pedimos desculpas&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; não estamos conseguindo recuperar &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; informações no momento&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; Por favor&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; tente novamente mais tarde&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;section&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 1);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `type`, `user_id`, `status`, `privacy`, `uri`, `cat_id`, `post_id`, `created_in`, `updated_in`, `description`, `key_words`, `image_featured`, `content`, `comment`, `number`) VALUES
(51, 'Introdução', 'doc', 9, 1, 1, 'introducao', 15, 0, '2020-05-20 20:11:42', '2020-05-20 22:25:44', 'Nopadi MF o micro-framework progressivo para a construção de aplicações web.', '', NULL, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Nopadi MF ou NP é um&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);&quot;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;micro-framework progressivo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; para a construção de aplicações PHP baseadas em rotas. O Nopadi/NP utiliza o conceito MVC para renderizar os recursos da aplicação. O Nopadi foi desenvolvido a princípio para construção de um e-commerce, mas com a sua implementação incremental de recursos, o seu desenvolvedor, decidiu abrir o seu código fonte. Apesar do Nopadi MF ser titulado de micro-framework, ele é capaz de lidar com grandes volumes de dados e é facilmente adaptável para projetos mais robustos. Em poucos minutos, você será capaz de criar um sistema de paginação para a sua API com poucas linhas de código. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);&quot;&gt;Veja o exemplo abaixo de uma paginação de dados utilizando o Nopadi MF no back-end e Vue.JS no front-end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Código Nopadi para disponibilização da API de paginação&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;Route&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;teste&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	 echo Paginate&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;np_posts&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;	&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Código HTML com as diretivas do Vue.JS&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;DOCTYPE html&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;html lang&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;pt-br&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;head&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;title&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Nopadi Exemplo&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;title&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;meta charset&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;UTF-8&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;meta name&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;viewport&quot;&lt;/span&gt; content&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;script src&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;js/vue.js&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;script&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;script src&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;js/axios.min.js&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;script&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;head&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;body&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;div id&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;app&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;section v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;errored&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Pedimos desculpas&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; não estamos conseguindo recuperar &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; informações no momento&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; Por favor&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; tente novamente mais tarde&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;p&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;section&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;section v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;div v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;loading&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Carregando&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;div&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;ul v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;ul&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n     &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;span&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Página &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;number&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; de &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;total&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; Total de registros&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;count&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;span&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	 \r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;ul&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	        &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;li &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;a  v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;previous&quot;&lt;/span&gt; href&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#&quot;&lt;/span&gt; @click&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;paginate(previous)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Anterior&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;a&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;li&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;li v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;(link, index) in numbers&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;a v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;index != number&quot;&lt;/span&gt; href&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#&quot;&lt;/span&gt; @click&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;paginate(link)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;  href&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;index&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;a&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;li&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;li &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;a  v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;next&quot;&lt;/span&gt; href&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;#&quot;&lt;/span&gt; @click&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;paginate(next)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Proximo&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;a&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;li&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n       &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;ul&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n     &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;li v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;post in itens&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;h3&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;post&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;title&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;h3&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	      &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;span v&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;html&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;post.content&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;span&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	 &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;li&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;ul&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;div&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;section&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;body&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;html&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Código JavaScript com Vue.JS&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;script&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token class-name&quot;&gt;Vue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  el&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;#app&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n      itens&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  previous&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  next&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  count&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  url&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  loading&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token boolean&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n      errored&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token boolean&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  number&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  total&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	  numbers&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n   &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;/*Aqui está a função para paginação*/&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  methods&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n     paginate&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;urlApi&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; \r\n      axios\r\n      &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;urlApi&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;\r\n      &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;response &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;itens &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;results&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;count &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;count&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;previous &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;previous&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;next &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;next&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;number &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;number&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;total &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;total&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;numbers &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; response&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;data&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;numbers\r\n	   &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;error &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n        console&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;error&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;\r\n        &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;errored &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token boolean&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;\r\n      &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;loading &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token boolean&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	 &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;/*Função de páginação será criada na montagem da aplicação*/&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;mounted&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;paginate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;http://localhost/nopadi/teste&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;script&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;O menor código de todo o processo acima foi o do Nopadi. É verdade que é necessário realizar algumas configurações antes de criar uma API com Nopadi, mas no geral, as confirações também são fáceis. No momento está em desenvolvimento o &lt;strong&gt;Nopadi Admin&lt;/strong&gt;. Ele será capaz de gerenciar o framework de forma gráfica. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 1),
(52, 'Criando uma rota', 'doc', 9, 1, 1, 'criando-uma-rota', 15, 51, '2020-05-20 23:53:43', '2020-05-21 00:36:56', 'Criando uma rota para um recurso de API.', '', NULL, '&lt;p&gt;A criação de rotas no Nopadi é bastante simples e utiliza uma sintaxe bem comum conforme os principais frameworks do mercado. As rotas no Nopadi podem ser utilizadas para renderizar um template do Motor Nopadi de template, ou simplesmente para processar um recurso especifico.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;No exemplo abaixo vamos criar uma rota para imprimir o nosso primeiro &quot;Hello World!&quot;. Para isso, navegue até o &lt;strong&gt;diretório &quot;app&quot;&lt;/strong&gt;, pois é no &lt;strong&gt;diretório &quot;app&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; que ficará armazenado toda a lógica da sua aplicação, incluindo as pastas para suas rotas, modelos, controladores e visualizadores.&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(63, 81, 181);&quot;&gt; MVC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;+R ou &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(233, 30, 99);&quot;&gt;MVCR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; (Modelo,Visão, Controle e Rotas).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Abra o arquivo &quot;web.php&quot; de rotas pelo seguinte caminho: &quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;app/http/routes/web.php&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&quot;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ao abrirá o arquivo &quot;web.php&quot; você encontrará o seguinte comentário:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;php\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;/*\r\n|--------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n| Rotas do Nopadi MF\r\n|--------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n| Nopadi MF é desenvolvido por: Paulo Leonardo da S. Cassimiro\r\n| Esse é o primeiro arquivo de roteamento a ser executado pela aplicação Nopadi\r\n|\r\n*/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Você pode apagar o comentário desse arquivo e começar a escrever a sua primeira rota.&amp;nbsp; Para isso vamos chamar o método estático &quot;get()&quot; da classe &quot;Route&quot;, e vamos passar dois parametos, sendo o primeiro o nome da rota ao qual você deseja renderizar e o segundo a função anônima ou closure que executara um código qualquer com a lógica que você escrever. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;?php&lt;br&gt; Route&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;minha-primeira-rota&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Agora acesse pelo seu navegar essa URL, não esqueça de verificar se o seu servidor PHP está funcionando. No meu caso, eu irei acessar essa rota pelo seguinte endereço :&quot;localhost/minha-primeira-rota&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Você provavelmente encontrará uma página em branco. Isso significa que a rota foi renderizada, porém como não há nada na função, o navegador por padrão exibirá uma página em branco. Caso&amp;nbsp; você digite uma rota que não exista o Nopadi apresentará mensagens informando que a rota não foi definida ou te levará para a pagina 404 caso o modo desenvolvedor esteja desativado. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vamos então criar o nosso primeiro &quot;Hello World!&quot;. Para isso, vamos escrever utilizando a função auxiliadora &quot;hello(&#039;Hello world!&#039;)&quot;. Para deixar as coisas mais interessantes, vamos passar um segundo parâmetro nessa função em forma de &quot;string&quot; com a seguinte escrita: &quot;success&quot;. com isso a saída será formatada com a cor verde. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;php\r\n  Route&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;minha-primeira-rota&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;\r\n    &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;hello&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;Hello World!&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&#039;success&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;Esse foi um guia básico para que você possa criar a sua primeira rota. O recurso de rotas é bem mais robustos, já que as rotas podem interagir diretamente com os arquivos de controles e visualizadores. Para aprender mais sobre rotas, leia o tópico roteamento, lá você saberá lidar com todas as possibilidades de rotas. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 2, 2);

